text: Herbert Lübking (born October 23, 1941 in Minden-Dankersen) is a former West German handball player who competed in the 1972 Summer Olympics. In 1972 he was part of the West German team which finished sixth in the Olympic tournament. He played all six matches and scored nine goals.Olympic results ==References== Category:1941 births Category:Living people Category:German male handball players Category:Olympic handball players of West Germany Category:Handball players at the 1972 Summer Olympics
